          <span class="text-2xl">📅</span>
          <div>
            <span class="block font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Lịch Vạn Niên</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-450 dark:text-slate-500">Tra cứu ngày âm dương, giờ tốt xấu hằng ngày</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/huong-dan-xem-bai-tarot-online-chinh-xac/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-brand-darkCard rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:shadow-md hover:border-brand-blue dark:hover:border-brand-mint transition">
